Metadata.Title: Serial Killer 2: Valentines Massacre
Metadata.Description:
We have nothing to go on here other then this serial killer was a bit different from the last New Years Eve Paris slayings. Again with nothing to go on other then eyewitnesses saying early on they saw a man dressed in all red carrying a red case walk up to two lovers on the dock and then they walked away quickly looking Ill, only to find one stangeled and the other drowned in a porto-potty.Only couples were killed this time around.  This isn't random, this man HATES Valentines day, or people in love.  However the diversity of kills match the Paris killings... or a bad 1980s slasher movie.

<HCCE>
